### ==========================================================
### Notification Service — 8 requests
### Flow: get VAPID key → list notifications → manage settings
### ==========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050
@accessToken = <paste-after-login>
@notificationId = <paste-notification-guid>

### 1. Get VAPID public key (no auth required)
# Clients need this to subscribe to web push notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/vapid-public-key

### 2. List notifications (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Get unread notification count
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Mark single notification as read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Mark all notifications as read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. Update notification settings
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "habitReminders": true,
  "friendActivity": true,
  "challengeUpdates": true
}

### 7. Register device for push notifications
# Valid platform values: web_push, expo_push
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "web_push",
  "token": "test-push-token",
  "deviceId": "test-device-1"
}

### 8. Unregister device (DESTRUCTIVE — run last)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "test-device-1"
}
